## Description {#details}

<code>MOVEM</code> is an instruction that moves multiple registers a time according to the given mask.

Thus sometimes it&#39;s pretty expensive. This file contains a pass that collapses sequential MOVEM instructions into a single one.

<SectionDefinition>
